in my first year of grad school.

144
00:14:53,726 --> 00:14:56,058
There was nothing between us.

145
00:14:56,128 --> 00:14:59,393
I knew his family.
I knew Leah.

146
00:15:00,165 --> 00:15:02,599
I mean, this thing,
this is kind of...

147
00:15:04,637 --> 00:15:06,696
kind of new between us.

148
00:15:06,772 --> 00:15:07,830
Wow.

149
00:15:09,642 --> 00:15:13,043
You're so sweet together.

150
00:15:13,112 --> 00:15:15,478
Of course,
I think the world of him.

151
00:15:15,547 --> 00:15:19,347
He's such a good man.

152
00:15:19,418 --> 00:15:21,352
Such a good father.

