157
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:46,944
Never lived East before.

158
00:15:47,012 --> 00:15:49,173
Kids'll get to see
their first ocean.

159
00:15:49,248 --> 00:15:52,012
Yeah, I'm afraid
downtown's falling apart.

160
00:15:52,084 --> 00:15:56,384
That's what I hear. I guess we're
not in Kansas anymore, eh, Toto?

161
00:15:56,455 --> 00:15:57,547
Hannah.

