164
00:16:10,803 --> 00:16:13,704
It's been a long time since
I've seen him just bein' a kid.

165
00:16:13,772 --> 00:16:15,569
Sometimes he's...

166
00:16:15,641 --> 00:16:18,075
You know, since his mother...

