00:16:19,979 --> 00:16:23,346
He has a tough time
making friends sometimes.

168
00:16:25,818 --> 00:16:27,877
Well...

169
00:16:27,953 --> 00:16:30,649
lucky we all need friends.

170
00:16:30,723 --> 00:16:33,021
Life just isn't the same
without 'em.

171
00:16:46,171 --> 00:16:48,731
Let me take this in. Dad?

172
00:16:48,807 --> 00:16:52,504
- Yeah?
- How do you spell "restricted"?

