175
00:17:01,253 --> 00:17:03,278
Building a compound.

176
00:17:03,355 --> 00:17:05,915
- Compound?
- Soldiers' compound.

177
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:09,625
Stop, Dad.

178
00:17:09,695 --> 00:17:12,289
You have to know
the secret handshake.

179
00:17:12,364 --> 00:17:14,298
Should we tell him?

180
00:17:16,969 --> 00:17:18,937
All right. Well...

181
00:17:19,004 --> 00:17:23,168
just so I know you're not gonna
use any fireworks in there, Brady.

182
00:17:23,242 --> 00:17:25,176
General Brady, Dad.

183
00:17:25,244 --> 00:17:28,680
Yeah?
No fireworks, General Brady.

184
00:17:28,747 --> 00:17:32,706
That's classified information.
