185
00:17:32,785 --> 00:17:35,845
- I'm serious, Brady.
- Come on, Grant.

186
00:17:37,456 --> 00:17:40,050
Get washed up, guys.
We're gonna get dinner on.

187
00:17:56,108 --> 00:17:59,271
- Come on in.
