194
00:18:17,062 --> 00:18:19,929
Must've lost track of some guy,
sent it to me instead.

195
00:18:19,998 --> 00:18:23,126
Sorry about the mess. Cheryl and the
girls are at a church group tonight.

196
00:18:23,202 --> 00:18:25,227
