Excuse me a minute. Hello?

200
00:18:39,184 --> 00:18:41,584
Why don't I call you back?

201
00:18:43,355 --> 00:18:45,289
What do you mean?

202
00:18:46,425 --> 00:18:47,858
Okay.

203
00:18:50,262 --> 00:18:53,322
