217
00:19:30,669 --> 00:19:32,762
You and Brooke, I mean.

218
00:19:33,939 --> 00:19:36,134
- I thank you, neighbor.
- For what?

219
00:19:36,208 --> 00:19:38,301
For having
a ten-year-old next door.

220
00:19:44,616 --> 00:19:47,779
- What do you know about shopping malls?
- Huh?

221
00:19:47,853 --> 00:19:52,415
Shopping malls. I was over at
the Langs', talking with Oliver.

222
00:19:52,491 --> 00:19:57,428
He had this blueprint on his counter.
He said it was the Reston Mall.

223
00:19:57,496 --> 00:20:00,192
- That's what he's workin' on.
- Yeah, but it wasn't.

224
00:20:01,266 --> 00:20:03,393
