225
00:20:03,468 --> 00:20:07,302
It was a building.
It wasn't a mall.

226
00:20:07,372 --> 00:20:10,136
- Right, it's an addition.
- No.

227
00:20:11,210 --> 00:20:13,644
It was an office building.
It wasn't stores at all.

228
00:20:13,712 --> 00:20:17,239
Oh, so, it's some other project
that he's working on.

229
00:20:21,753 --> 00:20:24,415
