231
00:20:28,193 --> 00:20:31,720
When you took engineering in college,
what kind of grades did you get?

232
00:20:31,797 --> 00:20:33,731
I didn't take engineering.

233
00:20:40,539 --> 00:20:43,770
What I saw was an office building.

234
00:20:49,381 --> 00:20:50,575
Fourteen moths <i>ago</i>
on a Monday in January...

235
00:20:52,150 --> 00:20:55,210
over 60 federal employees
went to work like they always <i>did....</i>

236
00:20:55,287 --> 00:20:58,415
at the Roosevelt Federal Building
in downtown St. Louis.

237
00:21:00,158 --> 00:21:03,218
Except on that Monday
they didn't come home.

